<%= content_for :main_wrapper_class, "small-width-padded-container" %>
<h2 class="standard-top-offset mb-4">Find the best articles about <span class="underline">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>.</h2>
<p class="mb-2">Convus is a place to find and share high quality writing, and discuss what the best articles on a given topic are.</p>
<p class="mb-2">Use it to understand out how other people think and where their opinions come from.</p>
<p class="mt-6 mb-2"><strong>How it works:</strong></p>
<ol class="list-decimal mt-3 mb-6 pl-5">
  <li class="mb-3">A topic is chosen every 3 days</li>
  <li class="mb-3">Review articles on the topic</li>
  <li class="mb-3">Vote on which articles on the topic are the best</li>
</ol>
<p class="mb-3">Reviewing is fast and doesn't require writing anything&mdash;install the <%= link_to "browser extension", browser_extensions_path %> and give it a try.</p>
